data.description: Private setting with mountain views on a quiet cul-de-sac amidst beautiful, natural vegetation, and “behind the gates” in Rumbling Bald on Lake Lure’s community. Recent updates include a newer roof, HVAC, hot water heater, luxury vinyl flooring, paint, kitchen and baths, and a fully fenced back yard. This home is just a short golf cart ride down to all resort amenities, including a private beach, indoor & outdoor pools, tennis/pickleball courts, 2 championship mountain golf courses, fitness center, full-service spa & salon, restaurants, bars and more. The main level features 2 bedrooms + a bonus guest room, living and dining areas, as well as the kitchen with a laundry closet. Off the living room is a fully finished unheated sunroom overlooking the mtns, and woods. Downstairs you’ll find a family room along with a bar area as well as a large walk-out unfinished space, currently used as a workshop and storage. There is a storage shed out back as well.
